00:23:46.384 --> 00:23:47.552 position:50% align:center
I'll be with you in a jif.

00:23:47.635 --> 00:23:49.721 position:50% align:center
Please take a seat
in the meantime.

00:23:54.768 --> 00:23:58.063 position:50% align:center
[CHIYUKI]
A manager? From another agency?

00:23:58.146 --> 00:24:00.607 position:50% align:center
This is the worst timing ever.

00:24:01.858 --> 00:24:04.694 position:50% align:center
[CHIYUKI] Ms. Akasaka, I can
come back again if you'd like!

00:24:04.778 --> 00:24:06.696 position:50% align:center
[AKASAKA]
Right, maybe some other time.

00:24:06.780 --> 00:24:07.947 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:24:12.827 --> 00:24:16.414 position:50% align:center
