00:25:38.913 --> 00:25:40.206 position:50% align:center
[CHIYUKI]
Wow.

00:25:42.000 --> 00:25:45.837 position:50% align:center
[CHIYUKI]
The star of today's shoot...

00:25:45.920 --> 00:25:47.714 position:50% align:center
